1. how to build myfirstapp (CA)

    cd $VSSDK/tee/tee_dev/tutorial/myfirstapp/build/ca
    make

    note: you may need to add armv7a-cros-linux-gnueabi- toolchain in your PATH
    export PATH=$PATH:$VSSDK/toolchain/aarch32/armv7a-cros-linux-gnueabi-4.9/bin/

2. how to build libsample.ta.clear TA (it's a clear TA)

    cd $VSSDK/tee/tee_dev/tutorial/myfirstapp/build/ta
    make

    note: you may need to add arm-eabi- toolchain in your PATH
    export PATH=$PATH:$VSSDK/toolchain/aarch32/gcc-linaro-arm-eabi-6.2.1/bin/

3. how to use test key to encrypt libsample.ta.clear

   cd $VSSDK/factory/scripts/bg5ct/ta_encryption/vendor_ta/sample
   ../bin/vendor_ta_encryption -i $YOURPATH/libsample.ta.clear -R TA_Root_Cert.rcert -m signing_test.cfg -C CustKey.bin -S ExtRsaKey.pem -o $YOURPATH/libsample.ta

   note: these keys and cert file in VSSDK are for testing only, do not use them for production

4. how to run myfirstapp
   1) flash ROMK image into a Synaptics board and boot up it
   2) copy myfirstapp and libsample.ta to /data
   3) cd data
   4) ./myfirstapp libsample.ta
   5) CA will load TA and inoke a command, you can see below message:
      succeed to invoke command 0x00000000
